detail_desc: Playsuit in soft viscose jersey in a double layer at the top with narrow shoulder straps, an elasticated waist and side pockets.
5-pocket jeans in superstretch washed denim with a regular waist and super-skinny legs.
Top in marled sweatshirt fabric with a print motif. Ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Polo-neck jumper in fine-knit premium cotton with ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Leggings in glossy, patterned jersey with an elasticated waist and elasticated foot straps.
Jumper in a soft, textured knit with a roll-edge neckline, long sleeves and a rounded hem with slits in the sides. Slightly longer at the back.
Long-sleeved dress in lightweight organic cotton sweatshirt fabric with a round, ribbed neckline, press-stud on one shoulder and a seam with a flounced skirt at the hem. Lightly brushed inside.
Top in sweatshirt fabric with a wrapover shawl collar, long sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Wide jumper in a soft, fine knit containing some wool with dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Fully lined bikini bottoms with elastication at the top and overlocked, scalloped edges. Extra low waist and cutaway coverage at the back.
5-pocket, ankle-length jeans in washed, stretch denim with hard-worn details. High waist, a zip fly and button, and skinny legs with raw-edge hems. The cotton content of the jeans is partly recycled.

Top in soft cotton jersey with textured stripes. Fake jetted pocket with a button at the top and a fabric appliqué above the hem. Narrow ribbing around the neckline and long sleeves with a sewn-in turn-up at the cuffs.
Knee-length, V-neck dress in soft viscose jersey with a collar and short sleeves. Seam below the bust with elastication at the back and sewn-in ties at the sides. Unlined.
T-shirt in printed cotton jersey with ribbing around the neckline.
Wide blouse in airy slub-weave cotton with embroidered details, a grandad collar and buttons down the front. Wide 3/4-length sleeves with buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem.

Short dress in woven fabric with a sheen. Wrapover V-neck, a concealed zip at the back, long puff sleeves and wide cuffs with covered buttons. Inset band with pleating at the waist and a flared, softly draping skirt. Partly lined.
Knee-length shorts in sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist, side pockets, a back pocket and raw-edge hems.
Long-sleeved top in soft cotton jersey with a text print motif on the front.
Long-sleeved top in soft, printed cotton jersey.
Dress in an airy cotton weave with woven stripes. Narrow, adjustable shoulder straps with bows, smocking at the top and a seam and flounce at the hem. Unlined.

Full-length, V-neck dress in heavily draping jersey with a slight sheen. Long shoulder straps that can be tied in various ways, elastication at the back of the waist and a raw-edge hem. Jersey lining.
Wide, cropped jersey T-shirt with a print motif on the front.
Small bag with a narrow shoulder strap and a zip at the top. Lined. Size 16x22 cm.
Ankle-length trousers in woven fabric with a high waist, concealed hook-and-eye fastener and zip fly. Side pockets and straight legs with creases.
Double-layered hat in a soft, fine knit with a reversible sequin motif on the front.
Slim-fit trousers in washed, superstretch twill with hard-worn details, front and back pockets and narrow, raw-edge, frayed hems.
Padded jacket in a patterned weave with a detachable, fleece-lined hood and zip down the front with a chin guard. Side pockets with a button and narrow elastication around the hood and cuffs.
Metal and plastic earrings in various sizes and designs. Length from 2.7 cm to 4.5 cm.

Pyjamas with a long-sleeved shirt and bottoms in soft cotton flannel with decorative piping. Shirt with notch lapels, buttons down the front, an open chest pocket and a rounded hem. Bottoms with an elasticated waist.
T-shirt in soft, printed cotton jersey.
Sunglasses with plastic frames and tinted, UV-protective lenses.
T-shirt in soft cotton jersey with a slightly wider neckline and a rounded hem.
Shorts in sweatshirt fabric with wide elastication and a drawstring at the waist, side pockets, a back pocket and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems.
Jumper in a soft, double-knitted cotton blend with a V-neck, low dropped shoulders and tapered sleeves.
Dress in soft, printed organic cotton jersey with a round, rib-trimmed neckline, short sleeves, gathered seam at the waist and gently flared skirt. Unlined.
Top in soft cotton jersey with a print motif at the top, a foldover polo neck and long sleeves.
V-neck top in a viscose weave with narrow, adjustable shoulder straps.
Vest tops in soft cotton jersey with a scalloped trim around the neckline and armholes.
Top in jersey crêpe. Round neckline with an opening and button at the top, gathered seams at the yoke and shoulders, and short butterfly sleeves.
Shirt in a cotton weave with a button-down collar and buttons down the front. Small chest pocket, short sleeves with sewn-in turn-ups, and a rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back.
Slippers with a wide, padded imitation leather foot strap, moulded insoles and chunky soles. Platform front 3.5 cm, heel approx. 5.5 cm.
Dungarees in washed, stretch cotton denim with a zip at the sides, adjustable straps that cross at the back with metal fasteners, and side and back pockets.
Ballet pumps in woven fabric with broderie anglaise. Concealed elastication at the heels, fabric linings and insoles and thermoplastic rubber (TPR) soles.
Pyjama bottoms in a patterned cotton weave with covered elastication and a drawstring at the waist and a fake fly.
Playsuit in soft viscose jersey with narrow shoulder straps, an elasticated seam at the waist and short, wide legs.

Trousers in a crisp pima cotton weave. High waist with a tab and button at the sides, a zip fly and button, and front and back pockets. Wide, tapered legs with an adjustable tab and buttons at the hems.
Leather sandals with an adjustable ankle strap with a painted metal buckle. Moulded nappa leather insoles and fluted rubber soles.

Long dress in transparent mesh embroidered with glittery thread with an opening and button at the back of the neck, gathers around the neckline and a gathered seam below the bust. Long, wide sleeves with narrow, buttoned cuffs and a wide skirt with seams and a wide flounce at the hem. Jersey underdress.
Knee-length skirt in airy chiffon with a high, elasticated, ribbed waistband. Lined.

Soft, non-wired bra top in ribbed fabric designed with the minimum number of seams for a seamless, comfortable feel against the skin. Adjustable shoulder straps and padded cups that shape the bust and provide good support. No fasteners.
Jumper in a fine-knit viscose blend with a boat neck and 3/4-length sleeves.
Sturdy hi-tops in imitation suede with mesh details, a padded edge and tongue with a loop. Lacing at the front, mesh linings and insoles and rubber soles.
V-neck top in airy jersey with a button placket, 3/4-length sleeves and a rounded hem with slits in the sides. Slightly longer at the back.
Tights with an elasticated waist. 60 denier.

Baby Exclusive. Set with a long-sleeved top and pair of trousers in soft organic cotton jersey. Top with a concealed press-stud on one shoulder. Trousers with an elasticated drawstring waist and ribbed hems.

Set with a top and pair of shorts in soft cotton jersey. Top with appliqués on the front and flounced sleeves that continue down the sides. Shorts with a decorative bow at the front, an elasticated waist with a small frill trim at the top and diagonal side pockets.
Fitted top in ribbed jersey made from an organic cotton blend with a deep neckline, decorative buttons and short sleeves.

Softshell jacket in windproof, water-repellent functional fabric with folded seams, reflective details and soft fleece inside. Detachable hood with a soft fleece lining, a stand-up collar and a zip down the front with a chin guard. Front pockets and elastication at the cuffs. Unlined. The jacket has a water-repellent coating without fluorocarbons.
Joggers in sweatshirt fabric with a washed look. Elasticated drawstring waist, fake fly, side pockets, a back pocket, and legs with decorative stitching and ribbed hems.
Zip-through hoodie in sweatshirt fabric with a soft brushed inside. Zip down the front and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. The cotton content of the hoodie is organic.
Shorts in stretch twill with a zip fly and button, and front and back pockets.
Calf-length, bell-shaped skirt in a patterned viscose weave with a high waist, concealed zip in one side and high slits in the sides. Unlined.
Fine-knit top in soft slub cotton with narrow shoulder straps and embroidered appliqués on the front. Ribbed hem and ribbed trim at the back.
Padded jacket with a detachable, padded, lined hood, high collar, zip down the front and side pockets . Lined.

Fitted, calf-length dress in sturdy jersey with a deep V-neck, gently draped pleats at the top, shoulder pads and long sleeves. Seam at the waist and a skirt with a sewn-in wrapover at the front. Unlined.
V-neck blouse in a soft viscose weave with a small, frill-trimmed stand-up collar, ties at the neckline with tassels at the ends, and raglan butterfly sleeves that continue down the sides.
Long-sleeved shirt in cotton flannel with a collar, buttons down the front and a yoke at the back. Open chest pocket, buttoned cuffs and a rounded hem.
Fitted, cropped, sleeveless top in a rib knit with wide, flounce-trimmed shoulder straps and a sweetheart neckline with gathers at the front.
Hairband in braided imitation suede with leaf and flower appliqués. Elastic at the back of the neck.
Long-sleeved top in soft cotton jersey with a text print motif on the front.
Calf-length dress in a patterned weave with a V-neck, adjustable spaghetti straps and slits in the sides. Lined.
Trousers in a cotton weave with a zip fly and button and side, back and leg pockets with a flap and concealed press-studs. Tapered legs with seams at the knees.
Slip-on trainers with elastic gores in the sides and a loop at the back. Imitation cork insoles and textured rubber soles.
5-pocket jeans in washed cotton denim with hard-worn details. Looser fit with a low waist and crotch, zip fly and button, and tapered legs. The cotton content of the jeans is partly recycled.
Joggers in lightweight, washed cotton twill with covered elastication and a drawstring at the waist, a fake fly and side pockets. Tapered legs with covered elastication at the hems.
Earmuffs in shimmering metallic imitation leather and faux fur with a soft, thermal fleece lining nearest the ears.
Ankle-length jeggings in soft, stretch denim with worn details. Extra-high waist, zip fly and button, fake front pockets, real back pockets and skinny legs.
Knee-length, printed swim shorts with elastication and ties at the waist and a fly with a hook and loop fastening. Soft mesh inner shorts.
Soft toy in a cotton knit with embroidered details. Polyester filling. Length approx. 18 cm.

detail_desc: 5-pocket, ankle-length jeans in washed stretch denim in a relaxed fit with a high waist, zip fly and button and straight legs with cut-off, raw-edge hems.
